description:
• Adjustable and removable padded shoulder strap with SGS
  • Outside and inside zippered pocket
  • Padded haul loop
description_long:
If you need a holdall that’s as comfy to carry as it is convenient to store away then the Eastpak Rollout is the bag for you. Suitable as carry-on luggage, the Rollout is essential gear for regular travellers. Its adjustable padded shoulder strap takes all the strain of your travel!
The Eastpak Rollout comes in a variety of colours and designs.

description_long:
Always ending up with more shopping than you had originally thought? This amazingly handy Eastpak Rollout is an eternal lifesaver. Perfect for regular travellers, it is neither too big as a suitcase, nor too small as a handbag. Use it for a weekend to the countryside or take it with you to your quick urban adventures! For optimal convenience, the Eastpak Rollout becomes even more practical thanks to its adjustable and padded shoulder strap.
A variety of different colours and patterns will undoubtedly charm you.

You can ballroom-dance in the airport hallway with this trolley if you like. Inside, the space is divided into two compartments to keep your luggage nice and tidy. The compact S-version comes handy for short city-trips. If you’re packing for the Bahamas, the M-version might suit you better.
